    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8037760>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Corethrella bifida sp. nov., female adult, allotype (MZUSP). A. Left palpus, lateral view. B. Flagellomeres and pedicel, lateral view. C. Cranial setae, anterior and posterior views, and clypeus in anterior view. D. Thoracic setae, lateral view. E. Hind leg claw and empodium, lateral view. F. Head, anterior view. G. Antenna, lateral view. H. Wing. I. Wing veins. J. Abdomen, lateral view. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8037760/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8037812>
    dc:description "Fig. 21. Corethrella davisi Shannon & Del Ponte, 1928. A. Adult cranial setae, anterior and posterior views, and female clypeus in anterior view. B. Adult thoracic setae, lateral view. C. Hind leg claw and empodium, lateral view. D. Larval exuvia, ventral view. E. Exuvia of larval head, ventral view, except mandible in dorsal view. F. Pupal exuvia, dorsal view. G. Pupal respiratory organ, dorsal view. H. Pupal methatorax and abdomen, dorsal and ventral views. Scale bars: 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8037812/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8037756>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Corethrella pindorama sp. nov., female adult, holotype (MZUSP). A. Head in anterior view. B. Cranial setae, anterior and posterior views, and clypeus in anterior view. C. Left palpus, lateral view. D. Flagellomeres, lateral view. E. Flagellomeres and pedicel, lateral view. F. Thorax and legs, lateral view. G. Detail of thorax, lateral view. H. Thoracic setae, lateral view. I. Wing veins. J. Wing. K. Hind leg claw and empodium, lateral view. L. Abdomen, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8037756/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8037776>
    dc:description "Fig. 10. Corethrella unifasciata sp. nov., female adult, holotype (MZUSP). A. Head, anterior view. B. Cranial setae, anterior and posterior views, and clypeus in anterior view. C. Left palpus, lateral view. D. Antenna, lateral view. E. Pedicel and flagellomeres, lateral view. F. Thorax and legs, lateral view. G. Detail of thorax, lateral view. H. Thoracic setae, lateral view. I. Wing veins. J. Wing. K. Hind leg claw and empodium, lateral view. L. Abdomen, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8037776/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8037766>
    dc:description "Fig.8.Corethrellapatashosp.nov.,femaleadult, holotype.A.Head, anteriorview.B.Cranial setae,anterior and posterior views, and clypeus in anterior view. C. Left palpus, lateral view. D. Antenna, lateral view. E. Flagellomeres and pedicel, lateral view. F. Thorax and legs, lateral view. G. Detail of thorax, lateral view. H. Thoracic setae, lateral view. I. Wing veins. J. Wing. K. Hind leg claw and empodium, lateral view. L. Abdomen, lateral view. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8037766/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8037770>
    dc:description "Fig. 9. Corethrella fuscifimbria sp. nov., female adult, holotype (MZUSP). A. Head, anterior view. B. Cranial setae, anterior and posterior views, and clypeus in anterior view. C. Left palpus, lateral view. D. Antenna, lateral view. E. Pedicel and flagellomeres, lateral view. F. Thorax and legs, lateral view. G. Detail of thorax, lateral view. H. Thoracic setae, lateral view. I. Wing veins. J. Wing. K. Hind leg claw and empodium. L. Abdomen, lateral view. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8037770/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

